Featuring a live wallpaper of Alita as the cybernetic warrior, this extension showcases her strength, courage, and determination as she battles through a futuristic world. Every new tab is an opportunity to be inspired by her unstoppable spirit.

Features:
🎨 High-quality live wallpaper of Alita, the cybernetic warrior, from Battle Angel Alita.
🌐 Customizable search bar to use your preferred search engine.
🕒 Clock and date display for a practical and stylish browsing experience.
🔗 Quick-access shortcuts to your favorite websites.
Let Alita’s bold and heroic presence empower your browsing experience, with each new tab reflecting her tenacity and strength. Ideal for Battle Angel Alita fans and anyone who admires a cybernetic warrior's relentless pursuit of justice.
